### Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:5217/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "erick",
  "email": "erick@example.com",
  "password": "123456789"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5217/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "erick",
  "password": "123456789"
}

### Crear Proyecto (necesitas el token del login)
POST http://localhost:5217/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
